@startuml sd_ReportService_getDepartmentSummary
skinparam backgroundColor #F9FAFB
title ReportService.getDepartmentSummary(yearMonth) - 部门工资汇总报表

actor "调用方" as Client
participant "ReportController" as Ctrl
participant "ReportService" as RptSvc
participant "DepartmentRepository" as DeptRepo
participant "SalaryRecordRepository" as RecRepo
participant "Department\n(实体)" as Dept
participant "Employee\n(实体)" as Emp
participant "DeptSalarySummary\n(DTO)" as DTO

Client -> Ctrl: GET /api/reports/department-summary?yearMonth=202403
Ctrl -> RptSvc: getDepartmentSummary(yearMonth)
RptSvc -> DeptRepo: findByActiveTrue()
DeptRepo --> RptSvc: List<Department>
RptSvc -> RecRepo: findByYearMonth(yearMonth)
RecRepo --> RptSvc: List<SalaryRecord>
note right of RptSvc #F0F8FF
  **分组汇总:**
  stream().collect(
    groupingBy(
      r→r.employee.department.id
    )
  )
end note
loop 每个部门
  DTO -> DTO: new DeptSalarySummary(deptId, deptName)
  note right of DTO #F0F8FF
  **汇总指标:**
  - 人数(count)
  - 应发合计(sum grossPay)
  - 个税合计(sum incomeTax)
  - 社保合计(sum socialInsurance)
  - 公积金合计(sum housingFund)
  - 实发合计(sum netPay)
  end note
end
RptSvc --> Ctrl: List<DeptSalarySummary>
Ctrl --> Client: ApiResponse → JSON\n[ {部门名, 人数, 应发合计, 实发合计, ...} ]
@enduml
